I never tasted durian before and I can guarantee that it will be the last time. 36 hdk for a small dessert with durian that I hated... 😅 There is another dessert restaurant just next door that is cheaper and is written in English 😅.
With plenty of desserts with local flavour
Not bad. Standard Chinese desert places.
It's seemly special for mango derived desserts.
A must try dessert place. So yummy and so many options in such a reasonable price. Go go go and try it!

差。落單後發現沒有貨, 沒有即時通知客人。要等到當客人等了一段時間後追問時才說出來。
